tool_description: Convert JSON payload to TypeScript definitions
name: Convert JSON to Typescript
title: Convert JSON to Typescript

api_list.name: Type
api_list.description:
Post JSON object to generate TypeScript types definitions for it.

In order specific cases to be handled, like union and optional types an array of objects could be provided.

api_list.name: Enum
api_list.description: Post an array of strings to generate enum definition

api_list.name: Interface
api_list.description:
Post JSON object to generate TypeScript interface definitions for it.

In order specific cases to be handled, like union and optional types an array of objects could be provided.
